high_descs: Walk ahead a few steps and then right, turning right at the stove to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk right to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and head ahead and then right to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge to the left of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk over to the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the closest potato off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left again and walk up to the microwave.
Heat up the potato in the microwave then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated potato in the fridge, then close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk in the direction of the wall directly ahead of you, hang a right to the long side of the island that is farthest from the fridge.
Pick up the potato sitting in front of the head of lettuce on the island.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave oven at the far end of the counter to your left.

Open the microwave door, place the potato on the right side of the plate in the microwave, close the door, turn the microwave on; when it turns off, open the microwave door, pick up the potato, close the door.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the potato on the shelf with the egg, to the left of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a potato, refrigerate the potato
